  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Badminton coach",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Badminton Coach Vacancy</strong></h2><p>We are seeking a <strong>qualified and experienced Badminton Coach</strong> to join our organisation. The successful candidate will be responsible for developing young athletes through structured training programmes and fostering excellence, discipline, and sportsmanship.</p><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>six (6) years of professional playing experience</strong> in badminton</p></li><li><p>Demonstrated <strong>competitive achievements</strong> (e.g. tournaments, rankings, awards)</p></li><li><p>Strong interest and commitment to <strong>coaching and youth development</strong></p></li><li><p>High level of <strong>professionalism, responsibility, and dedication</strong></p></li><li><p>Effective <strong>communication, interpersonal, and motivational skills</strong></p></li></ul><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Plan and conduct <strong>structured badminton training sessions</strong> for young students</p></li><li><p>Design and implement <strong>skill-based drills and development programmes</strong></p></li><li><p>Monitor and evaluate students’ progress and prepare them for <strong>competitive play</strong></p></li><li><p>Promote <strong>discipline, teamwork, sportsmanship, and positive values</strong> through sport</p></li></ul><p>Candidates who are passionate about developing young talent and contributing to a professional training environment are encouraged to apply.</p><p><strong>Application Details:</strong><br />Interested applicants may submit their <strong>curriculum vitae and relevant achievements</strong> to:<br /><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">yb.sportacademy@gmail.com</a></p>",
